data.description: Charming townhome one block from the University. This meticulously maintained home is ideal for students or faculty seeking convenience and comfort. The well-designed layout creates a seamless flow between living spaces. Abundant cupboards and counter space along with a pantry make the kitchen optimal. Relax in the living room with the warmth of the fireplace. Two masters with bathrooms, tile and LVP flooring, high-end door handles and fixtures provide functionality and style. The private backyard with it's beautiful red tree and cement patio make for a relaxing outdoor living space. Did I mention no HOA dues? Three to five minutes to multiple grocery stores, restaurants, and Old Town. Get to the freeway in under ten minutes. Homeowners are moving due to corporate relocation. Call to schedule a private tour, get the market analysis, and seller's preferred term sheet.
